        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-89",
        "content": "Alarmed, but not discouraged, she tried it another way; a bolt flew, and she believed herself successful; but how strangely mysterious!",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
